            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="table-row">
            <div class="table-cell tc-6">
                <img src="~/lib/Images/SamuraiSpirit/penalty-support.png" class="talenticon" />
                During turn, cannot choose Support action
            </div>
            <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="table-row">
            <div class="table-cell tc-6">
                <img src="~/lib/Images/SamuraiSpirit/penalty-left.png" class="talenticon" />
                Neighbor adds a card to <i>combat line</i><sup><span class="asterisk"></span><span class="dagger"></span></sup>
            </div>
            <div class="table-cell tc-6">
                <span class="asterisk"></span> If unable to apply penalty, take a wound instead
                <br />
                <span class="dagger"></span> Talents cannot be applied, but Kiai may activate
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


